"%(new_line)s%(new_line)sType %(bold_start)s@username%(bold_end)s to mention "
"someone, and grab their attention.%(new_line)sType %(bold_start)s#channel%"
"(bold_end)s to mention a channel.%(new_line)sType %(bold_start)s/command%"
"(bold_end)s to execute a command.%(new_line)sType %(bold_start)s::shortcut%"
"(bold_end)s to insert a canned response in your message.%(new_line)sType %"
"(bold_start)s:emoji:%(bold_end)s to insert an emoji in your message."
msgstr ""
"%(new_line)s%(new_line)sNapíšte %(bold_start)s@username%(bold_end)s, aby ste "
"niekoho spomenuli a upútali jeho pozornosť.%(new_line)sNapíšte %(bold_start)"
"s#channel%(bold_end)s, aby ste spomenuli kanál.%(new_line)sNapíšte %"
"(bold_start)s/command%(bold_end)s, aby ste vykonali príkaz.%(new_line)"
"sNapíšte %(bold_start)s::shortcut%(bold_end)s, aby ste do správy vložili "
"prednastavenú odpoveď.%(new_line)sNapíšte %(bold_start)s:emoji:%(bold_end)s, "
"aby ste do správy vložili emoji."

